main event: A strange object was found in a field near Fort Washakie, Wyoming in 1961.
interesting points: The object was observed hovering at an altitude of about 300 feet, was approximately 40-50 feet in diameter, and made of a dull silver metallic material.
The object had a dome on top and no visible protrusions, ports, windows or other appendages.
The object remained motionless for 10-15 minutes before suddenly shooting straight up and disappearing from sight.
Several witnesses, including a 24-year-old man, reported the sighting.
The Air Force was unable to definitively identify the object, but determined it did not pose a threat to national security.
sighted object: a large, silver metallic object with a dome
